Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:37.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 这里是日暮家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 戈薇 考试怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:42.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:44.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:46.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚饭还来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:48.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就吃大餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拜托你买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:56.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:02:02.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样观赏着美丽的枝桠 真是沁人心扉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:06.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇那家伙 还没回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:08.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 去接她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:12.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:19.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨 搞坏我盆栽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:20.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:22.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:24.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:27.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:29.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:32.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她说考试也考完了 今晚要吃大餐庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:33.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买得有点多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了 今晚犬夜叉也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 这饭太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:54.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生平以来 曾否试过如此安稳地进餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 放心地慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:00.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这是多么好吃的饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:07.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉有时候很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:09.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我回来晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:11.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:14.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天要吃大餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你准备好食材了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:17.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我来宰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:24.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锦…锦鲤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:25.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见它们在游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在别人家的水池里面游是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:32.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么嘛 我辛辛苦苦捉回来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:37.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快退后 老衲把它宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:03.05,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀的碎片{\fad(130,130)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在留意那井啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天戈薇不是要回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我考完高中入学试马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然今天犬夜叉去接她了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:25.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:31.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算戈薇回来了 净化之力也还被封印着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片被污染了的琥珀还在昏睡中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:38.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他还一直不吃不喝地睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:42.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 俗话说「睡得多长得快」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见大人没怎么睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你根本没长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是堂堂的大妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在杀生丸斩杀曲灵之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:55.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀都不会醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真的很久没这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能在我身边这么长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:07.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他醒不来 也比分开而更安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人 你能写字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:12.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是「女孩」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:15.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:16.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「公主」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「姐姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「妹妹」是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「媳妇」是这样写的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像全都是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:27.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然变黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法…法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回家里去 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是奈落的手下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:40.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是曲灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:50.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲灵的味道 很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:59.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗅着曲灵的些许恶臭 远道而来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:02.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸大人的鼻子的确灵敏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦幻之白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？左臂？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没有吗 又长出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:12.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:16.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 还是那么刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只对这家伙有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:24.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:32.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然无法斩杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就尽情打吧 杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个曲灵是我弄出来的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的曲灵现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等不祥的邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心琥珀他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带村民们去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:53.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:04.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 风穴使用过度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:06.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口又会扩大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:08.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑影没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:21.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪是幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的真正目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪见大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有奇怪的影…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:37.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:50.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到被曲灵占据了身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个小鬼的最后的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉就能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…把琥珀还来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:01.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完事了就把这身体还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意是具尸体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:09.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附上他身后我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:14.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼是靠碎片维系生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:18.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙想连同琥珀的身体把碎片送给奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪也不会让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:28.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 曲灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:34.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用那风穴把小鬼吸进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会吸你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白费功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:09:00.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要被污染的碎片还在这里 我的力量就是无限的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为可以把我吸收殆尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 法师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吸了人不能吸的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:12.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸了恶灵的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:14.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 请你也去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我送你上路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 故意这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:34.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:35.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 玲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:40.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是附在琥珀身上的曲灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:42.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为你 把厨房和大餐都弄得一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:58.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我已经道歉很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况有奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有血和毒的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在枫的家那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫婆婆的家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塌了 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:19.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚 伤得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:25.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…去追琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见我这丑态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘴气的伤扩散到胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:43.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然用了药老毒仙的药 感觉不到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像干得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒 你的风穴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘴气之伤和风穴哪个先要我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:03.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 都已经快到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 跟你说过多少遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:10.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉 现在不是说这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去追琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们安安分分地在这里待着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:15.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:18.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:31.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的气味明明没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失态了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是气味的源头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:54.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是被你斩下的曲灵的肉片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:58.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾上了没来得及逃跑的灵魂的气味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够用来拖住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你察觉得有点迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:11.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 你得再陪我一会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还被你小看了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:19.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为用这些喽啰能拖得住我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以我召集了一千只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？瞬杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于被曲灵附身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:43.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀的碎片被污染得比以前的都要肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得帮枫大人重新建好屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:05.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:07.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤…疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:14.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是留在弥勒身边比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:18.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺走琥珀的碎片 奈落一定会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:22.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 只要打倒奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒就会解除 法师大人的风穴便会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:34.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有分出胜负 才能打破这窘迫境地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这不是杂物房吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说牢骚话了 小妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:46.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲这家伙 没有醒来的迹象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:51.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果这事给杀生丸大人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的性命就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是万分抱歉 杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:58.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有我邪见跟着…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是除妖师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:06.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:09.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直睡着 但没感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝了抑制痛苦的药…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:18.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能与我并肩作战 他喝了药老毒仙的药
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:22.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要还能感受到痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得…风穴都快要吞噬自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:36.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我们两人独处一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:42.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我也要赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:45.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲碰到了曲灵的毒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:49.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做驱灵的药汤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:56.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直为了我和琥珀而伤害自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:14:59.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:21.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片云是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:22.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想夺走琥珀的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金刚枪破
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:36.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来夺回碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把这小鬼砍成碎末吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于没有实体的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼只不过是个容器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被污染的碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要净化那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:09.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人 你忘了你的灵力被我封印了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连破魔之箭的力量也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗的法术也对我无效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且四魂之玉即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀 醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:31.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为醒来后会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:33.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:39.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道被污染得漆黑的四魂之玉在让琥珀看着些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:45.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:53.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:55.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:58.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:07.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…和大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀犯下的弥天大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了父亲和同伴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在四魂之玉的力量作用下反复体验着那一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昏睡后一直这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:21.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:26.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使醒来了 琥珀的心也会崩溃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:30.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经崩溃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 你也要醒来 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是残酷的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:43.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来的话 我会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在要战斗 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:50.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你说什么 都太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…我做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:07.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:54.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 姐姐没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:00.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又伤害了姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人也因为想救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…法师大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:22.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:28.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命？由我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:19:59.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认得出我吗 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:09.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:11.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀的碎片里面 有光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:16.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:20.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲灵 虽然你一直强调桔梗的法术对你无效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像并非一点用没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:28.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗的光转到琥珀的碎片上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:34.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 把我从过去带回来的是桔梗大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:37.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还来得及 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 你是想自杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会恐惧而离开你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:07.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以操纵缠着碎片的碎肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚周围
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你逃跑之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:14.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉和姐姐会夺回碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:18.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会落到你手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:20.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:23.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 老是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被逼迫出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会交出碎片的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:28.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:33.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移到琥珀的碎片上的桔梗的光在给予他力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:38.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把曲灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:40.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:41.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得及…还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
